<li id="cite_note-80"><b><a href="#cite_ref-80" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.kcna.co.jp/item/2006/200608/news08/11.htm#5" class="external text" title="http://www.kcna.co.jp/item/2006/200608/news08/11.htm#5" rel="nofollow">"Film 'Diary of a Girl Student', Close Companion of Life"</a>, Korea News Sercive, 10 August 2006.</li>
